{"type": "article", "id": 4214, "title": "不倒翁酒杯", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-09T07:39:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233157u4doQ7WlTYhiNJpX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t与三五好友或是工作中需要打交道的客户、同事吃饭时，最担心出现意外情况，比如打翻了酒杯或者饮料杯，麻烦的同时，还免不了尴尬。日前，设计工作室 Superduper Studio 为此设计了一款名为「Spillproof 」的酒杯，它摒弃了传统高脚酒杯的支架以及底座设计，而是沿着酒杯底部的外沿部分向下往内缩小，这样的设计使得酒杯即便发生倾斜，也不会出现整杯被打翻的情况，活像一个不倒翁。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233155oxCacw1jvQ0ZtT5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.871875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233155wUzTjmE6H1834Rgv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9234375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331557oLTKD0shFElyNm1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.975\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233156kH4Co8yqIds1TYfa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523315691kQ87rfgsJF06Sh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}